name: CompositeMap_containsValueTest
description: Unit tests for the containsValue method in CompositeMap.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_ValuePresentInFirstMap
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value present in the first map.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_ValuePresentInSecondMap
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value present in the second map.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_ValueNotPresent
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value that is not present in any map.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_AfterAddingNewMap
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value after adding a new map to the composite map.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_AfterRemovingValue
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value after removing it from the composite map.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_AfterPuttingNewValue
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value after adding a new map with a new value to the composite map.
